                                   "description":  "Akai gains a 25( +5% Total HP) shield for 4s on each skill cast and marks enemy heroes and Creeps hit by his skills. Akai\u0027s Basic Attacks deal 25( +5% Total HP) extra (Physical Damage) to marked enemies.",
