                                  "comboUsage":  "",
                                  "strategicPurpose":  "",
                                  "iconName":  "Headbutt",
                                  "tips":  "The long-ranged jump allows for a strong engage into the enemy back line, a narrow escape across walls or just a really good ambush. Remember that when enemy\u0027s are marked by Blender (with the Froggy symbol floating on their heads) jumping on them will stun them.",
                                  "iconUrl":  "/raw-assets/skill_icons/akai/headbutt.png",
