                                    "tips":  "Hurricane Dance is Akai\u0027s disruptive skill. Aside from the annoying knock back and wall pinning, Akai is immune to slowdown effects and has increased movement speed during the ULT duration. Akai\u0027s ULT also works as a Purify which clears all CC and Stun effects on him.",
